data.description: Welcome to 1315 N Main Street, This cute as-a-button Cape Cod is in South Strabane Twp and Trinity Schools. Home sweet home is what you should think upon entry, The home features 3, possibly 4 bedrooms and 1 full bath with laminate flooring throughout the main living space. Welcome yourself through the relaxing flow of the main level, complete with a nicely sized kitchen and light-filled dining room. then sit back and take a break in the living room in front of the fireplace. When summer hits, you will be ready for dinner on the back deck or take a swim in the pool to cool off those hot summer days.
